    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit worn over bumps. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic flaws and the need for some upcoming maintenance.",
