    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for a dedicated new owner to bring it back to its former glory. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity for someone looking for a budget-friendly project or a valuable source of parts. If you love a challenge and have the skills to match, this is the perfect canvas for your next automotive adventure!",
