    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, making it an ideal candidate for a dedicated project or a parts donor. The engine and transmission require significant mechanical attention and are not currently reliable for daily use. Visually, the exterior has substantial rust, several large dents, and significant paint oxidation, while the interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery. Please be prepared for a vehicle that needs extensive repairs before returning to the road.",
