    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an unparalleled example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-grade condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an immaculate, smoke-free interior. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and reliability. Meticulously maintained and kept in optimal conditions, this specimen represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a definitive, high-caliber vehicle without compromise.",
      "price": 46500.0,
